# .trivyignore — Forge-Scan documented exceptions for Trivy IaC scanning.
#
# Each entry MUST include rationale + intended fix or explicit "permanent".
# Re-evaluate quarterly. Remove an entry when its tracking PR lands.
#
# Format: <ID>     # <rationale>
# Re-run locally with:
#   docker run --rm -v "$PWD:/work" -w /work aquasec/trivy:0.51.2 \
#       config --severity HIGH,CRITICAL .

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Network scanner — runAsUser:0 + NET_RAW + NET_ADMIN are operationally
# required for raw-socket SYN scanning. See deploy/kubernetes/base/scanner-
# deployment.yaml > forgescan-network-scanner. The scanner is otherwise
# locked down (drop ALL caps, allowPrivilegeEscalation:false, readOnlyRoot,
# seccompProfile RuntimeDefault) and runs in its own namespace with strict
# NetworkPolicies. Permanent — until a userspace packet capture replaces raw
# sockets.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
AVD-KSV-0011   # CPU not limited (network scanner — capped by node sizing)
AVD-KSV-0012   # Runs as root user (raw-socket requirement)
AVD-KSV-0020   # Runs with low UID (raw-socket requirement)
AVD-KSV-0022   # Capabilities NET_RAW / NET_ADMIN added (raw-socket requirement)

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Hetzner / external scanner Docker Compose — uses host networking + raw
# socket caps for the same reason as the network scanner above. Compose is
# only used for single-tenant external deployments behind STLink.
# See deploy/hetzner/docker-compose.yml.
# Permanent.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
AVD-DS-0014    # Use of host networking (compose requirement)

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Plaintext placeholder secret in deploy/kubernetes/base/database.yaml.
# Operators replace this at deploy time via SealedSecrets / external-secrets;
# the literal "CHANGE_ME_USE_STRONG_PASSWORD" exists only to fail loudly
# when forgotten. Tracking: doc/customer-onboarding-checklist.md step 4.
# Permanent.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
AVD-KSV-0151   # Plain-text Secret literal (placeholder by design)
